name: Mixed Feelings
description: Grape has never been so ANGRY to see Grape, who has never been so HAPPY to see Grape, who has never been so MISERABLE to see Grape, who has never been so APATHETIC seeing Grape, who has never been so SHOCKED to see Grape, who has never been so UPSET to see Grape, who has never been so LONELY after seeing Grape, who has never been so CONTENT staring at the sky.
